# Naming conventions for Sharepoint Lists and Libraries

## Column Types
- Single text
- Lookup fields
- Selected Option(s)
- Available Options(s)

### Single text
Content is limited to 256 characters

### Lookup fields
Relationship with other list, using a record Id.

Name format: LocationId

Advantage: query columns from connected list
Disadvantage: not suitable for lists changable in time

### Selected Option(s)
Single text field which stores Title or any other identification data.

Name format: ImagesOptUid
Data format: CH1;CH2

## Available Option(s)
Single text field (if the length is enough).

Name format: ImagesOptAvailable
Data format: GROUPA=CH1|CH2;GROUPB=CH3|CH4
